data.description: Welcome home! This home has old charm with newer amenities! Tall ceilings, beautiful woodwork and wood floors on the main level. Newer kitchen with new gas range. The main level primary with an ensuite featuring separate jetted tub and shower! Great front porch full of windows. Fenced in yard with a spacious deck. Tons of storage space.
